{"tid":2397814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"暗網 Dark Web 只有罪案呢啲嘢？記者實測上暗網版社交平台：「這裏有免於被政府監控的自由！」","createTime":"2021-02-06T17:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T08:41:22.000Z","uid":1886,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0124e9c97fcd564be335ef65f9c3262d956b7a","tid":2397814,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:53:50.000Z","msg":"毒品、槍械、買兇殺人和兒童色情，提到「暗網」（Dark Web）的時候，是不是只會讓你聯想起這些形形色色的罪案呢？<br />\n<br />\n相對於大部份可以用Google搜尋引擎找到、用一般的瀏覽器就能訪問的表網絡（Surface Web），暗網指需要使用特定的瀏覽器，才能登陸的特定洋葱區域，即字尾是「.onion」的網站。當中暗網背後的「洋葱路由」技術，本來是一套美國海軍人員在九十年代開發的流量暱名化技術，目的是為了保護軍方通訊的隱密性，後來才以自由軟體授權的方式，並公開了原始碼，被軍方以外的民間人員廣泛應用。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_P80q-mUYqA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_P80q-mUYqA&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMITv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=189fcac2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_P80q-mUYqA</a></p>"},{"pid":"6fc15f417f523035dc3071a595f04046103d7b81","tid":2397814,"uid":81113,"like":13,"dislike":8,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"Deep web 幾時變咗dark web我唔知嘅?"},{"pid":"70d3b5eb3c9183222a709a7e43e2af44a6bbdd7f","tid":2397814,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:55:54.000Z","msg":"早前WhatsApp修改私隱條款，引致大量用家刪除WhatsApp及facebook，紛紛轉用其他的社交平台和通訊服務商，但隨即也引起部份人反思，萬一轉投的這些平台有天坐大，會否像今天一樣再次出賣用家呢？轉用其他平台，似乎也不是個一勞永逸的方法。而在一個總統會被社交平台集體封殺；科技大企業出賣用戶私隱；敏感資訊網站被下架處理，種種迹象都在在地反映，似乎表網絡在保護私隱和言論自由道路上，已經漸趨凶險。<br />\n<br />\n當我們關心通訊私隱，而轉用Signal和MeWe；當我們關心交易私隱而入手Bitcoin等虛擬貨幣；但當我們關心的，是一整個網絡私隱和自由時，會不會有一天，暗網也會成為主流呢？比起法外之地的刻板印象，你又會否對暗網稍微改觀呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210203/MTBWVZPCYJH4XHXDKBKUOF4KDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210203%2FMTBWVZPCYJH4XHXDKBKUOF4KDU%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMITv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=5599a3a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210203%2FMTBWVZPCYJH4XHXDKBKUOF4KDU%2F&h=5d55a65d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210203/MTBWVZPCYJH4XHXDKBKUOF4KDU/</a>"},{"pid":"19631d0b86daf99ab23d1d8698f7899903e46991","tid":2397814,"uid":370061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:56:36.000Z","msg":"其實大都數都係用嚟買野啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543121064dfc28697fba4e4577d81c67c8b509e0","tid":2397814,"uid":171107,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6fc15f417f523035dc3071a595f04046103d7b81","tid":2397814,"uid":81113,"like":13,"dislike":8,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"Deep web 幾時變咗dark web我唔知嘅?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:58:29.000Z","msg":"曼加拉效應"},{"pid":"6a095d165271b5a98e65e1fb8e7ec5bd474bd8dd","tid":2397814,"uid":202256,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"6fc15f417f523035dc3071a595f04046103d7b81","tid":2397814,"uid":81113,"like":13,"dislike":8,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"Deep web 幾時變咗dark web我唔知嘅?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:59:47.000Z","msg":"兩樣嘢嚟<br />\nDeep web係正常search engine 搵唔到嘅嘢<br />\n好似YouTube 啲private 咗嘅片<br />\n你要有link先入到<br />\nDark web 都係deep web嘅一種<br />\n但只包括係要特殊browser 先用到<br />\n但啲人用得多deep web<br />\n當deep web係dark web咁用"},{"pid":"d67e1ce4f6630f703ad4cab4430e06b102c892f3","tid":2397814,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:59:59.000Z","msg":"Robert W Gehl是猶他大學的副教授，長年關注社交網絡的生態，並曾在2018年推出以探索暗網社交網絡的專書《Weaving the Dark Web》。他在2015年的文章〈Socializing the Dark Web〉中，訪問了暗網社交平台Galaxy的站長，一位化名為「Lameth」的男性。問到為甚麼有人會大費周章，使用暗網社交平台時，Lameth回答只要有人的地方，自然就會有交流的需要，暗網也不例外，自然也需要一個互相交流的平台。"},{"pid":"4a0a7d076538852f68a446fb9e0aac5214e76b7c","tid":2397814,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"作為站長，Lameth進一步地說到，包括該站的成員，許多暗網使用者本身並非犯罪分子，而只是重視私隱和言論自由的人。他說我們不會希望政府和大財團，闖進家門翻箱倒櫃地翻遍你全屋，而這就等於表網路，現今網路的現狀。現在人們於表網路的一舉一動，都在政府和大財團的監控下無所遁形，已經沒有隱私和自由可言，而暗網就是防止這種監控的工具。"},{"pid":"c790224688f582e4d93815d763be7436175c5b38","tid":2397814,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"6a095d165271b5a98e65e1fb8e7ec5bd474bd8dd","tid":2397814,"uid":202256,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"6fc15f417f523035dc3071a595f04046103d7b81","tid":2397814,"uid":81113,"like":13,"dislike":8,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"Deep web 幾時變咗dark web我唔知嘅?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:59:47.000Z","msg":"兩樣嘢嚟<br />\nDeep web係正常search engine 搵唔到嘅嘢<br />\n好似YouTube 啲private 咗嘅片<br />\n你要有link先入到<br />\nDark web 都係deep web嘅一種<br />\n但只包括係要特殊browser 先用到<br />\n但啲人用得多deep web<br />\n當deep web係dark web咁用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T18:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r8Nt14q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr8Nt14q.gif&h=69a8d073&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"420ef67353c2518113efe6c9a181d30ccb02b25c","tid":2397814,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T18:10:55.000Z","msg":"記得中學問同學借咗恐懼鳥本deep web睇 睇完嚇撚到仆街 驚咗幾個月 訓覺都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後有個同學真係上咗去 好多變態核突野 真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d900f9dae93592195fdf52f43ac6ef9a2ea27e01","tid":2397814,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"420ef67353c2518113efe6c9a181d30ccb02b25c","tid":2397814,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T18:10:55.000Z","msg":"記得中學問同學借咗恐懼鳥本deep web睇 睇完嚇撚到仆街 驚咗幾個月 訓覺都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" c